    <p style="margin-left: 380px; margin-top: 30px;">Some information about the Famous painting</p>
    <div class="container d-flex me-4 mt-0" style="background-color: #b2d8d8;">
      <div class="card mt-5" style="width: 14rem; height: 100px; margin-right: 20px;">
        <img
        src="images/card1.webp"
          class="card-img-top" alt="card-1" style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">The Storm on the Sea of Galilee</h5>
          <p class="card-text">This painting is Rembrandt’s only seascape, and it’s famously known for being stolen in
            1990 and never recovered. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt-5" style="width: 14rem; height: 100px; margin-right: 20px;">
        <img
        src="images/card2.webp"
          class="card-img-top" alt="card-1" style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">A Bar at the Folies-Bergère</h5>
          <p class="card-text">This painting is celebrated for its complex play of gaze, reflection, and the ambiguities
            of modern urban life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt-5" style="width: 14rem; height: 100px; margin-right: 20px;">
        <img
        src="images/card3.webp"
          class="card-img-top" alt="card-1" style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Wanderer above the Sea of Fog</h5>
          <p class="card-text">An iconic painting of the Romantic period, it encapsulates the feeling of the sublime,
            facing the infinite and the unknown.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt-5" style="width: 14rem; height: 100px; margin-right: 20px;">
        <img src="images/card4.webp"
          class="card-img-top" alt="card-1" style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Las Meninas </h5>
          <p class="card-text">Velázquez’s complex and mysterious composition is a masterclass in perspective and a
            commentary on the act of painting itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt-5" style="width: 14rem; height: 100px; margin-right: 20px;">
        <img
        src="images/card5.webp"
          class="card-img-top" alt="card-1" style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">The Battle of Alexander</h5>
          <p class="card-text">This monumental work captures a legendary battle between Alexander the Great and Darius
            III of Persia.(Albrecht Altdorfer).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
